headline: Jacobs Solutions (J) Surges 4.6%: Is This an Indication of Further Gains?
summary: Jacobs Solutions (J) saw its shares surge in the last session with trading volume being higher than average. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions may not translate into further price increase in the near term.

headline: Jacobs to Hold Its Fiscal Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2025 Earnings Conference Call and Webcast
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) plans to release its fiscal fourth quarter and full year 2025 earnings results before market open on Thursday, Nov. 20, 2025, and will host a conference call at 10:00 a.m. ET, during which management will make a presentation focusing on the company's results and operating trends.
